>My problem:
>Let two circles with radii R1>R2.
>The circles are to a distance each other.
>I know how to make a geometrical construction for an outer tangent 
>line of the two circles.
>But how can I make a geometrical construction for an inner tangent?
>Thank you in advance.
>Fotis
>
>[Difficulty]
>
>
>[Thoughts]
